[title]Input Recorder[/]
[subtitle]Record and play back keyboard and mouse input[/]
A small [b]GUI-application[/] that makes it easy to [b]record[/], [b]play back[/] and share [b]keyboard and mouse[/] input in shape of a [b]macro[/].
Windows only.

[s1]Features[/]
1. Record [b]mouse movement[/] and [b]mouse buttons[/]
2. Record [b]keyboard input[/]
3. [b]Play back[/] recorded macros
4. [b]Save and load[/] recorded macros
5. [b]Restrict[/] recorded macros to be playable [b]once only[/]